{"tid":1039074,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 財困清潔工飲清潔劑　倒臥仁濟醫院士多房不治","createTime":"2019-02-27T07:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T23:21:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b8e3ae7dbd48f425a843745470f04b532a1ff197","tid":1039074,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"荃灣仁濟醫院C座大樓，今早(27日)10時40分，一名姓黃(34歲)外判清潔男工，在4樓「仁濟醫院－香港浸會大學中醫教研中心(仁濟)」士多房內，發現其姓沈(38歲)男工友倒臥地上昏迷，立即向醫護人員求助及報警。沈其後被送往醫院急症室搶救，惜最終證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報趕至，封鎖現場調查，並檢獲一封遺書，內容大致透露近日受金錢問題困擾。警方經初步調查後，相信男事主服用清潔劑自殺，事件無可疑，死者死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190227/bkn-20190227104705400-0227_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190227%2Fbkn-20190227104705400-0227_00822_001.html&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=fa48ed3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190227/bkn-20190227104705400-0227_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bf480a51eff50ae404a5085b4825d2198db11f1c","tid":1039074,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:18:41.000Z","msg":"買左 瑞聲？"},{"pid":"a2c9f1628c013b5b5128a5295077a4b94817432d","tid":1039074,"uid":130695,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:19:48.000Z","msg":"所以話唔返工問政府拎錢仲爽過返工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母交稅養大陸閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98505403533de0413d37b240dc6c903c9dc4a2d2","tid":1039074,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:20:10.000Z","msg":"bitcoin+瑞聲+吉利+舜宇"},{"pid":"1aa4ba01ee97801fc04b0a252f3410003d4f39f4","tid":1039074,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a2c9f1628c013b5b5128a5295077a4b94817432d","tid":1039074,"uid":130695,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T07:19:48.000Z","msg":"所以話唔返工問政府拎錢仲爽過返工<br 